data.description: This residence offers an appealing blend, making it an ideal dream home for first-time buyers seeking a valuable estate opportunity. Beautiful back deck with a huge sunroom. A house that is not only perfect for you and your family but spaciously enough to entertain for the holidays. It allows the new homeowner to receive passive income with a fully finished basement. The house comes with a separate entrance and parking. The home is located on a corner lot. This home checks all the boxes - a perfect lot, excellent floor plan, updates on kitchen and baths in a location convenient to everything. It is located just minutes from I-20 and minutes from downtown Covington.
